Eurovision Song Contest country profile

2025-05-02

North Macedonia

Participation and successes

North Macedonia has participated in the Eurovision Song Contest 21 times. It made it to the final round 9 times - thats 42.9%.

North Macedonia has won 0 times. Its most successful performance took place in the 2019 semi-final-2, when the country got 9.8% of all possible points.
